creator: Alaa Senjab
descriptionHtml:
Sinjab Academy is the first virtual academy for ophthalmology education. Our mission
is to simplify the concepts in ophthalmology and provides all levels of ophthalmologists and optometrists with all that they need in their practice.

Using this app, you will be able to:
- Access the Library and watch all the videos from the app.
- Access the Forum to post your cases, questions, reply to others, and much more!
- Register in the upcoming events.
- Connect with other fellow ophthalmologists and optometrists.
- Get notifications for new events, courses, tips, and forum discussions.
- And much more!

Tried the app already? Share feedback at support@sinjabacademy.org

Share the knowledge and leave us a review!
